WEBVTT

00:10:29.880 --> 00:10:33.040
We cannot teach our girls
until we teach ourselves.

00:10:33.960 --> 00:10:35.856
So here's another thing:

00:10:35.880 --> 00:10:38.976
fear and exhilaration

00:10:39.000 --> 00:10:40.760
feel very similar --

00:10:41.760 --> 00:10:44.336
the shaky hands,
the heightened heart rate,

00:10:44.360 --> 00:10:45.736
the nervous tension,

00:10:45.760 --> 00:10:47.496
and I'm betting that for many of you

00:10:47.520 --> 00:10:50.336
the last time you thought
you were scared out of your wits,

00:10:50.360 --> 00:10:53.296
you may have been feeling
mostly exhilaration,

00:10:53.320 --> 00:10:55.280
and now you've missed an opportunity.

00:10:55.720 --> 00:10:56.920
So practice.

00:10:57.560 --> 00:11:00.536
And while girls should be getting
outside to learn to be gutsy,